{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/writing-markup-with-jsx/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#jsx-putting-markup-into-javascript-%EC%9E%90%EB%B0%94%EC%8A%A4%ED%81%AC%EB%A6%BD%ED%8A%B8%EC%97%90-%EB%A7%88%ED%81%AC%EC%97%85-%EB%84%A3%EA%B8%B0\">JSX: Putting markup into JavaScript, 자바스크립트에 마크업 넣기</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#the-rules-of-jsx\">The Rules of JSX</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#1-return-a-single-root-element\">1. Return a single root element</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#2-close-all-the-tags\">2. Close all the tags</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#3-camelcase-all-most-of-tags\">3. camelCase <del>all</del> most of tags</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\">참고</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>","timeToRead":2,"html":"<blockquote>\n<p><strong>- 주의 -</strong> <br /> 정리하면서 저의 생각도 많이 넣는 편입니다. <br /> 혹시나 제 글을 읽으실 때 아리송한 부분이 생기신다면 해당하는 공식 문서를 꼭 참고하시길 바랍니다. <br /> 또한, 저에게 익숙한 내용들은 생략하고 정리합니다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>JSX는 자바스크립트 파일에서 HTML스러운 마크업을 작성할 수 있도록 해주는, 자바스크립트를 확장한 문법이다. 많은 React 개발자들이 JSX의 간결함을 선호하여 많이 사용하고 있다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"jsx-putting-markup-into-javascript-자바스크립트에-마크업-넣기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#jsx-putting-markup-into-javascript-%EC%9E%90%EB%B0%94%EC%8A%A4%ED%81%AC%EB%A6%BD%ED%8A%B8%EC%97%90-%EB%A7%88%ED%81%AC%EC%97%85-%EB%84%A3%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"jsx putting markup into javascript 자바스크립트에 마크업 넣기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>JSX: Putting markup into JavaScript, 자바스크립트에 마크업 넣기</h2>\n<p>많은 시간동안 HTML과 자바스크립트 코드를 다른 파일로 분리하여 사용했다. 하지만 점점 시간이 흐를수록 웹은 더 많은 상호작용을 요구하고, 로직에 따라 컨텐츠가 변경되는 일이 잦아졌다. 이것이 React가 렌더링하는 로직과 마크업을 컴포넌트라는 공간에 같이 넣는 이유이다.</p>\n<p>이렇게 한 공간에 둠으로써 로직이 변경되면 마크업도 변경되도록 동기화시킬 수 있다. 동시에 관련 없는 다른 컴포넌트의 마크업은 따로 분리되어 있으니 변경되지 않는다. 즉 자신의 로직이 변경될 때 자신의 마크업만 변경되고 다른 컴포넌트의 마크업은 건드리지 않는다. 이렇게 됨으로써 더욱 코드가 안전해질 수 있다.</p>\n<p>이러한 JSX는 HTML과 유사하게 생겼지만 조금 더 제한적이면서도 동적인 데이터를 보여줄 수 있다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"the-rules-of-jsx\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#the-rules-of-jsx\" aria-label=\"the rules of jsx permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>The Rules of JSX</h2>\n<p>JSX문을 작성할 때 알아야 할 몇 가지 규칙을 알아보자.</p>\n<h3 id=\"1-return-a-single-root-element\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-return-a-single-root-element\" aria-label=\"1 return a single root element permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. Return a single root element</h3>\n<p>컴포넌트에서 여러 요소를 반환하려면 하나의 부모 태그로 감싸야 한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"tsx\"><pre class=\"language-tsx\"><code class=\"language-tsx\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 올바르지 않은 예시</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">Temp</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">Im Jun</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">Frontend Developer</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 올바른 예시</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">Temp</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n      </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">Im Jun</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n      </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">Frontend Developer</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n    </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>div 대신 마땅한 태그가 없다면 Fragment로 불리는 &#x3C;>&#x3C;/> 태그를 사용하면 된다.</p>\n<p>이렇게 감싸야 하는 이유는 하나의 자바스크립트 객체를 반환하기 위해서이다. <a href=\"https://legacy.reactjs.org/blog/2020/09/22/introducing-the-new-jsx-transform.html#whats-a-jsx-transform\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">JSX문으로 작성해도 결국엔 React가 자바스크립트 객체로 변환한다.</a> 자바스크립트의 함수에서는 1개의 값만 반환할 수 있다. 올바르지 않은 예시처럼 작성하면 다음과 같이 될 것이다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"tsx\"><pre class=\"language-tsx\"><code class=\"language-tsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">Temp</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createElement</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'h1'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Im Jun'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createElement</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'div'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Frontend Developer'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>React에서는 이를 하나의 배열이나 객체로 묶지 않는다. 따라서 하나로 묶기 위해 이를 포함할 수 있는 부모 태그로 감싸서 반환해줘야 한다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-close-all-the-tags\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-close-all-the-tags\" aria-label=\"2 close all the tags permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. Close all the tags</h3>\n<p>HTML 작성하듯이 끝나는 태그가 있어야 한다. <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;img /></code>과 같은 셀프 클로징도 가능하다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"3-camelcase-all-most-of-tags\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-camelcase-all-most-of-tags\" aria-label=\"3 camelcase all most of tags permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. camelCase <del>all</del> most of tags</h3>\n<p>JSX문에서 태그의 속성으로는 보통 카멜 케이스로 작성해야 한다. 대표적으로 class가 있다. 다음과 같이 작성해야 한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"tsx\"><pre class=\"language-tsx\"><code class=\"language-tsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">Temp</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">className</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>profile<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n      </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">Im Jun</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n      </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">Frontend Developer</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n    </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이렇게 속성이 조금 변경되는 면이 있다. 하지만 data-*, aria-*와 같은 속성들은 역사적인 이유로 그대로 사용하거나 여전히 -를 사용하고 있다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"참고\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\" aria-label=\"참고 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>참고</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://react.dev/learn/writing-markup-with-jsx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Writing Markup with JSX</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://legacy.reactjs.org/blog/2020/09/22/introducing-the-new-jsx-transform.html#whats-a-jsx-transform\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Introducing the New JSX Transform</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"[React 공식 문서 타파하기] Writing Markup with JSX","summary":"React에서 JSX는 무엇인지, 어떻게 사용해야 하는지 알아봅니다.","date":"2023-05-01","categories":["React"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/4ade5cac5aba1b2a6129e12ce9a93deb/debc3/react-logo.png","srcSet":"/static/4ade5cac5aba1b2a6129e12ce9a93deb/e6d27/react-logo.png 1250w,\n/static/4ade5cac5aba1b2a6129e12ce9a93deb/f4108/react-logo.png 2500w,\n/static/4ade5cac5aba1b2a6129e12ce9a93deb/debc3/react-logo.png 5000w","sizes":"(min-width: 5000px) 5000px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/4ade5cac5aba1b2a6129e12ce9a93deb/55a90/react-logo.webp 1250w,\n/static/4ade5cac5aba1b2a6129e12ce9a93deb/a9708/react-logo.webp 2500w,\n/static/4ade5cac5aba1b2a6129e12ce9a93deb/f1cef/react-logo.webp 5000w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 5000px) 5000px, 100vw"}]},"width":5000,"height":1679}},"publicURL":"/static/4ade5cac5aba1b2a6129e12ce9a93deb/react-logo.png"}}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/writing-markup-with-jsx/","previousPost":{"title":"[React 공식 문서 타파하기] Importing and Exporting Components","slug":"/importing-and-exporting-components/"},"nextPost":{"title":"[React 공식 문서 타파하기] JavaScript in JSX with Curly Braces","slug":"/javascript-in-jsx-with-curly-braces/"}}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}